fields.name: Palms Beach
fields.description: Palms beach is often referred to as a family beach. It’s a place for everyone, young and old, with it being the closest beach to the city centre. Its names sake comes from the many Palm trees that are everywhere along the beach. The Palm trees provide shade to all that go there, which also is something that attracts the sun safe families as most of the other beaches in the area don’t have sufficient shade.

fields.name: Chilly Hills
fields.description: Past Oak Park you come to Chilly hills. These hills are home to many small communities who prefer to live in the countryside rather then in the city itself. In the winter they get covered in a thick layer of snow that takes the fancy of many of the town folk who come to the hills to take on the ski slopes. In the summertime the hills are covered in numerous wild flowers and small green meadows, a favourite too many of the city’s children for fun picnics and games.

fields.name: Beach
fields.description: With water so clear that you can see the fish below you and golden sand that seems to go on for miles. The town's folk favourite beach location, the blue water beach is a perfect place to go and relax. This beach is liked by many of the town's folk because it’s so calm and generous in size. The town’s people love to go snorkelling and see what the underwater sea life is like with all their beautiful colours that can be seen through the amazingly clear water.

fields.name: Daisy Highway
fields.description: Not far out of town are the daisy fields. The fields are split by Melvin’s favourite track the Daisy highway. He can’t think of a better way to spend his weekend then out on the daisy fields. He really likes how he can still see the city whilst all around him were beautiful fields of flowers and green grass. Years ago these fields were filled with daisies as far as the eye could see however as the years went by the daisies become less and less and now there is only small patches of daisies found spotted through the fields.

fields.name: Oak Tree Park
fields.description: The old park land known as Oak Tree Park is a perfect place for a quiet walk out in nature. The large oak trees that are the park's namesake provide the perfect backdrop that will make you forget all your worries. There are a number of pathways to explore, winding around the different nooks and crannies within the park lands. The paths were originally created by order of King Rupert’s great, great, great grandfather King Wilson who had the paths made for his wife as a wedding gift.

fields.name: Barren Lands
fields.description: The barren land on the other side of Chilly hills is somewhere very few adventure too. No one lives on the south side. Those who are more adventurous and spend some time out in the wilderness sometime travel across to the south side of Chilly hills and camp, however with no good camping spots nor any watering holes they don’t stay long.

fields.name: Chilly Hills (Snowy)
fields.description: As winter sets in on Chilly hills you can see the winter wonderland that the town’s folk love so much. The small little huts can be seen tucked away in the snow, providing a home to many who choose to live in the little communities outside the main city.

fields.name: Daisy Fields
fields.description: Daisy fields is such a peaceful place that if you are in the city and looking away from it you could easily forget that it's there all together. You don't have to travel far another way from the big city's noise and can easily get lost with the beauty of the fields themselves. However if you turn back towards the city the tall building stand out from the fields showing how close you really are to the big city.

fields.name: Mountain Forest
fields.description: Looking to where daisy fields meet Chilly hills in the spring time gives an amazing array of colours, showing off the true beauty of nature. This particularly so in the early part of spring where often the snow is still on the high points of the mountains with the colourful array of flowers starting to show their heads throughout the daisy fields.

fields.name: Oak Tree Park (Autumn)
fields.description: Oak Tree Park is not just beautiful in the summer and spring time, it becomes a whole new place in the autumn when all the leaves turn a beautiful orange with the change of season. The park is very popular at this time of year with the town autumn festival being held at the park. It’s a highlight for many of the townsfolk with it being one of the key get together for both young and old.

fields.name: Wings Wetlands
fields.description: Wings wetlands is just the place for a quiet stroll, albeit a little of the beaten track. It's a beautiful place to visit with most locals forget it's there, leaving those who still know of it and its beauty to enjoy it for themselves. King Rupert had many of the tracks around the wetlands fixed up to make them safer for the town’s folk to use in his quest to get them more active. Yet he didn’t get to publicise his efforts before he went missing.

fields.text: I may be a snail, but even I know its time to get moving today!
It may be early, but lets test out these new parts I bought!
A morning I enjoyed, what else is left in the day?
This old snail is eager for more!
My shells not broken yet! Lets take it to the track!
Two laps down, two to go! Think you can win?
Halfway there, quick refuel and We're good to continue!
No point buying these parts if we are only going to go halfway.
If tomorrow is like today, I think ill need to give my mechanic a raise!
Almost burned through a whole tank today, this is going to be a great relationship!
You seem to have endless energy! This old snail needs a little break though.
I think you earned the rest of the day off, tomorrow bright and early though!
Engines upgraded, you to thank. Lets kick off today in style!
Lets make it a sprint today!
No point sitting in the garage, fresh day ahead of us!
Used to get tired by now, But this new engine, come on another lap!
And they say snails are slow, lets prove them wrong.
You warmed up my engines, lets see who wins the race this time.
Four laps down, four to go. Making progress!
That hare would have napped by now, lets make him regret it!
Tanks getting low, we could wait till tomorrow to finish, unless you got more in you?
Always surprised by your effort, Make an old snail live again!
I see talent in you, but your holding just a little back still I can tell!
Ahhh, engines flat for the day, Keep this up and that hare wont know what hit him!
Thanks for the day, proved yourself a great partner!
Engines warm, Leaving my snail trail in the dust!
Never thought I would get this far!
Ten laps down, ten to go! Who would have thought I'd get this far.
If that hare ever took a nap again, I think we could lap him. Twice.
Lets make that last half in half the time!
When we met I was a slow snail, You got me in shape. Thanks
That hare, not a chance he will win another race again. Thanks
This snail has you to thank. Ill pay my dues on the race course.
Ready for my Training Flight Cap’n
First flight of the day. Lets take ‘er up!
Engines raring Cap’n. Just waiting on you!
Engines warm now, another round?
Let’s go another lap of the country Cap’n!
Refilled my tank, Another flight when you’re ready Cap’n!
Halfway up Cap’n lets keep going!
No point in quitting today, to the Summit!
Cap’n half way to our goal, lets push through!
TortleCopters around the world watch in awe at our flight!
Just like today, I KNOW tomorrows flight will be amazing!
Best flight I’ve had this week Cap’n!
This tortlecopter’s day has been made! Take a rest Cap’n
Tanks empty Cap’n, Thanks for the great day!
Come on Cap’n, new engines are raring to go!
Cap’n, we gonna fly anytime soon :(?
New engines installed, can’t leave me in the hanger all day!
Mmmm engines are warm, let’s take it up a notch?
Come on Cap’n, we can do better than that!
Only half way up, Tanks still half full!
Half a tank, no stopping us now!
Cap’n storms ahead, Let’s go right through!
Engines roaring! Thanks Cap’n
Wow Cap’n, was a great view up there!
Been a while since a flight like that. Thanks Cap’n
Fuels out, Best flight ever Cap’n!
Refueling time, same time tomorrow?
C’mon Cap’n,  New ski’s to test out!
We should go for a fly today Cap’n!
How about another flight around the mountains!
These new skis are working wonders! Let’s go another round!
Cap’n! You can’t be done already!
How about a race Cap’n? 20 minutes GO!
We can go a bit more I bet Cap’n
Tortlecopter to flight tower: Halfway lets pick up the pace!
This Tortlecopter is spoilt for sure!
Cap’n you spoil me with a flight like that!
I can already feel tommorrows flight will be EVEN better!
Been a pleasure flying today!
Couldn’t have asked for a better Cap’n!
Small break for me Cap’n, Tomorrow's gonna be GREAT!
This knight has training to attend to, Join me!
Let’s not waste the morning squire!
Sharp sword and a full tank, I believe it’s time for Training!
Brilliant session, but we have just begun!
I feel as if you’re not giving everything squire!
We can’t dally! The king is relying on us squire!
Merlin didn’t give me these powers to quit halfway!
No turning back now, Push Forward!
Great day squire, tomorrow will be great too!
Surprised me squire, Great work!
Not a step too few! The king would be proud!
Never have I ever, a day to be remembered squire.
Onwards to victory squire, you earned it.
My new powers need some practice, let’s go out squire!
We’ve come this far squire, let’s not waste the day!
Another goal ahead of us squire, let’s start the day strong.
My lightning and fire have only just warmed up, what about you squire!
Today has just begun, these new powers need more work!
Take a small rest, we march later today!
Halfway to our goal squire, halfway towards a day of glory!
We cannot quit halfway in! Let’s push through!
Great performance squire, if only everyday were like this!
You earned a rest, but you have a little more left don’t you?
A great day, a great journey, Squire I salute you!
This knight’s day has been made, thanks to you.
Never forget todays glory squire, you earned my thanks!
Ah, today was great. Tomorrow had better be as good!
Haven’t had a day like this for a while, good job squire!
Proud of the effort squire, great work!
I think you’ve earned that rest squire.
When I thought you couldn’t get better, surprised!
Not long until Merlins power is back online. Thanks!
My powers are back. Let us put them to work!
A long road we have traveled, but a new day is upon us. Let’s go squire!
No matter their numbers, we won’t quit halfway!
Strong session, these flames are eager for more though!
A small warm up squire, let the real work begin.
Half the day, half the work. Let’s keep it up!
Push through, same distance back as forwards so let’s CHARGE!
You have a little left still don’t you think squire?
Those legs wont earn themselves, lets get started!
Nails are polished, I'm ready to go!
These spots were made for walking, So lets go do just that!
A great start, but I think we could go a little more
This cheetahs paws are barely roughened, lets get back out there!
Nails are fine, we can go a little more!
I won't be outdone by a snail, lets keep going!
Great day! I'll have those legs in no time
If we can do that now, imagine what we can do with my new legs!
I bet Melvin is wishing he was here now, great day!
Spring in my step, lets start the day strong!
Don't even need to tend to these nails, lets get right out there!
Eager to see how far I can leap! Lets get going!
These springs work great! Lets put them to the test.
Nails still in check, lets push them further!
Melvin's lapping us! We can't leave that be lets get to it!
With my new springs and with your help, we'll never fail, Great day!
Melvin's probably jealous with the day we just had!
Great day! Give me a rest to clean my springs.
Even after all that my nails are fine! Great day!
My new turbine is ready for day, Lets burn some tracks!
Lets get out there, if you think you can keep up!
All that work together, lets go even further
Warmed my springs up, I got more to give, how about you?
Light run, I think we can turn it up a bit more.
Melvin's miles behind, lets get even further ahead!
Greatest partner there is, thanks for the day!
Time to rest for me, great day!
My springs need an oil change, lets go again tommorrow
Early rise, lets go get some honey!
I think now's the perfect chance to get out early and bring back a haul!
This bee will wait for no one, lets go!
Nice haul! I think we can manage a few more don't you think?
The hive is really loving that last haul, lets bring 'em more.
Ah its great to be out and about, lets keep at it!
Nice haul! I think we can manage a few more don't you think?
The hive is really loving that last haul, lets bring 'em more.
Ah its great to be out and about, lets keep at it!
Great day, we fed the whole hive just by ourselves!
I can't wait to see how much honey we get tomorrow!
This bee's tired, you sure know how to keep a hive stocked!
Bigger tank, Bigger hauls. Lets get started
Gonna need start getting more honey for the hives expansion!
Morning start, I feel up to it! Care to join?
One tank, Two tank, Three tanks more!
Great work, I think we still got a few more in us yet!
Keep it up, we'll have extra honey for weeks at this rate!
Everyone's loving the honey, I think we can rest for the day!
Great job, couldn't have a better partner!
I hope your keeping your fluids up after a day like that! Great Job!
New engine and a new day, Lets get started!
Lets triple our honey hauls! No time better to start then now!
Early bird gets the worm, Early bee gets the honey! Lets go!
Fastest haul ever! I wonder how many more we can get today?
Great start, I think you got more in you though!
Don't stop now, we could make this day our best!
Been a long day, You earned your rest partner.
The hive is amazed at the amount of honey we got, Great job!
Same time tomorrow? I bet it will be as great as today was!

Times have changed since Melvin was a young man! He is experiencing a world of great technological advancement... almost an unnatural amount.  He is sick of being considered an old, slow and out of date snail. His family is vastly wealthy and Melvin has noticed many other pet kingdom inhabitants with cybernetic components, and has decided that he himself should invest in this technology. However, he cannot achieve complete cyberisation alone and has requested your help in obtaining the various components he needs. What's in it for you? Money and friendship!

Having grown up on the slow-moving, slothful Turtle Isles, Sheldon grew envious of the quicker creatures, especially those who could fly. He once lost a bet with a hare about which of them would win a running race, even though the hare had been so arrogant as to sleep during the race! Sheldon came to a conclusion: as a turtle, he saw no way to remedy his natural evolution in order to obtain the speeds and flight he so desired. That is, until now! Recently Sheldon has been provided with the rotors and abilities of a helicopter. However, Sheldon’s technological cyberisation is not yet complete, and he requests your help in obtaining the various other components he needs.

Sir Oinksalot, the noble boar knight, a true hero throughout the pet kingdoms, and kingsguard and adviser to King Rupert. When he first joined the kingsguard he was gifted the powers of lighting and fire by Merlin the Magpie (yes... magpie), but this magic has taken a terrible toll on Sir Oinksalot's body. Under the advice of the king and other advisers, he has been told to seek out the components to make himself a cyborg in order to maintain control over his body.  But he cannot do this alone! King Rupert has issued a royal requisition for assistance, will you answer the call?
Needs to keep up his training to become the strongest!

As a small little bee, Bluebell always looked forward to the day she could go out and collect honey with the rest of her friends. But it turned out she was too overweight to fly. Devastated bluebell looked to the professor for answers. After 4 days of experiments bluebell left his laboratory with a new lease on life, and a new mechanical flotation device to boot! Now she begins her quest to be the best honey gatherer of the hive.

Zoe used to enjoy and easy life in the safari, then tragedy struck and she broke a nail. She just couldn't live with her self after this happened so she started lounging around. When king rupert came and motivated the pets of the land to be active she found a new lease in life, along with her new goal. She's saving up money to purchase mechanical legs with titanium nails so she will never break a nail again.

fields.name: Light Snails Race
fields.overview: When the going gets tough the tough get going. In the light snails race you are to uses your endurance to take some steps between now and the end of the day. This is one of Sir Oinksalot favourite challenges to partake in. With him liking how it requires him to push himself that extra mile. To be able to complete the challenge before the end of the day.

fields.name: Hardcore Snails Race
fields.overview: When you are keen to kick your endurance training up to the next level its time to take on the hardcore snails race. Though you are not sprinting along, take your time and get your steps count up. Just keep moving and before you know it you will have reached your goal.

fields.name: Hop a long
fields.overview: Take a jump in the right direction and hop into a hour long challenge. Its a perfect way to fill in a hour and work yourself and your pet. This challenge challenges you to move quickly over a longer period of time. To take on the task of reaching the goal before the timer runs out. This is what Sir Oinksalot really likes about this challenge.

fields.name: The hare and the tortoise
fields.overview: Both speed and endurance and needed to get through this one. You need to be quick on your feet however don't forget you have a goal to reach. You can't let the timer bet you before you have the all the steps required to complete the challenge. You may even see Melvin along the way as this is a challenge in which he often takes up, so keep your eyes open.

fields.name: Tortoise Tail
fields.overview: Taking one step at a time its time to see where this tortoise's tail will lead you. You'll never know until you take it up and see. This challenge will get you moving over the next 2 weeks, looking to see if you can complete the challenge. This is no time to rest so don't forget.

fields.name: Rolling like a pig in mud
fields.overview: Pigs like to roll in the mud every day so you need to see if you to can keep your steps up in the long run. As this is going to be a long run, keep count and see if you can reach the mark before time runs out. If you are looking at not meeting it try and get 10 000 or more steps each day and before you know it you will be there.

fields.name: Buzzing along
fields.overview: Buzzing along to see if you can keep the buzz on for 3 days. Its the bees favroute actives to do, as its got a real buzz to it. Its the type of challenge that before you know it its all over, so why not take it for a flight and see if you can get your buzz on?

fields.name: Take Flight
fields.overview: Its time to reach for the sky and to see where the skies can take you away over the next two days. Don't let the sky be your limit uses this an challenge way to take yourself that little extra. So don't let something stop you for achieving your goals.
